wminc-prefinfo-language: Tuji 'interface'achi bhas - Tuji wiki topasnne-kin veglli
wminc-prefinfo-code: Tu jea bhasacher kam kortai tachi 'ISO 639 code'[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO 639]
wminc-prefinfo-project: Tu hangasor khuimchea Wikimedia projectacher kam kortai?
wminc-prefinfo-error: Tuven ji bhas nivoddlai, taka ISO codeachi goroz asa
wminc-error-wronglangcode: '''Chotrai:''' Hea panacher asleli [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|eka bhasechi ISO code]] sarkem na "$1"
wminc-error-wiki-exists: Hi wiki soddhea ostitvant asa. Ti tuka hea panar mevteli: $1. Hi wiki atach suru zalea zalear thode horam vo thode dis rav soglleo panam ieunk.
wminc-error-wiki-sister: Hem pan jea wikicher asa ti hanga na. Hea wikik hanga sod: $1
randombytest: Wiki topasnnechi khoincheim adlem modlem pan
randombytest-nopages: Tujea wiki topasnnent ekui pan na, hea nanv-zageant: $1
wminc-viewuserlang: Vangddiachi bhas ani wiki topasnni sod
right-viewuserlang: Vapurpeachi bhas ani wiki topasnni polloi
wminc-code-macrolanguage: [[wikipedia:$2 language|"$3" language]] zaun asa ISO 639 pormonem ek [[wikipedia:ISO 639 macrolanguage|vrut-bhas]]. Tem him bhasecho zomo zaun asa:
wminc-code-collective: "$1" hem code eke khaxel bhasek nhoi, bogor ek bhasecho zomo, mhonnge [[wikipedia:$2 language|"$3" bhaso]].
wminc-code-retired: Hem bhasecho ISO code bodol'lam ani atam mull bhasek lagu zaina.
wminc-listusers-testwiki: Tum polletai apli wiki topasnni $1 mhunn tharailele vapurpi.
wminc-search-nocreate-nopref: Tuven "$1" sodlai. Upkar korun tujeo [[Special:Preferences|wiki topasnnechi posonti]] tharai, hea vorvim amchean tuka khoinchem pan rochunk zai tem sangunk zata!
wminc-search-nocreate-suggest: Tuven "$1" sodlai. Tu tujea wikint pan rochunk zata hangasor: [[$3]]
wminc-searchwiki-noresults: Kai porinam na. Tujean bhasecho code vo nanvam vorvim sodunk zata. Bhasechem nanv teach bhasen, tum Incubatoran uzar kortai ti bhas, vo Ingles bhasen zaunk ieta.
wminc-searchwiki-multiplematches: Tujem sodak heo panam mell khatat:
wminc-fs-intro: {{SITENAME}} hachem poilim pavlance avtam-an tuka ievkar. Tuka novi wiki suru korpachi ritiche vatt dakhoilelem zatelem.
wminc-fs-signup-text:
Tuje kode poile pasun khatem asa zalear [$1 sotrorombh kor]. Na zalear, upkar korun [$2 khatem roch].
Khatem rochpachem soktichem nhoi, pun kelear borem mhonn updes ditanv, ani hem korunk thodoch vell lagta.
wminc-fs-settings-text:
Upkar korun atam [[Special:Preferences#mw-htmlform-i18n|hangasor tujeo wiki topasnnecheo posonti]] dorz kor.
Poili zaun asa tuji site uzar korpachi bhas, ji tuven poili pavlan nivoddlai, pun tuven ti bodlunk zata.
Dusri zaun asa jea prokolpan tuka borounk zai and tisri zaun asa tea prokolpachi bhasechem code.
Tum code nokloi zalear, upkar korun amchem [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-manual-url}}|hath-pustok]] vach vo [[{{MediaWiki:Portal-url}}|adar]] mag.
wminc-fs-userpage-text: Upkar korun atam tujem vapurpiachem pan $1 roch, ani tantun svotache babtint kai mullavo mahiti boroun. Haka duvo panache voir tuka distolo.
wminc-fs-globaluser-text: Tujem khatem zaun asa thollavo. Tuka updes ditanv teka jogatik kor mhonn $1 vorvim. Oxem toren tujean hem khatem khoincheim Wikimediachi wikint uzar korunk zatelem.
wminc-fs-startwiki-text: Tuji wikichem nanv $1-an suru zata. Wikichem Mukhel Pan rochun tujean wikicho orombh korunk zata hanga sor: $2.
wminc-fs-startwiki-exists-text:
Tuji wiki $1-an suru zata. Mukhel Pan hanha asa: $2. Tujean atam hea bhaseche dusre vangdiank mellun somudai bandunk zata!
Tuka pan rochunk zai zalear, fokot voilea chovkottan boroi, ani tuka distelem to duvo click kor.
